                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <p class="ss-home-schedule-note">
                  <i class="bi bi-clock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  Youth runs 5 PM Mon/Tue/Wed/Fri. Adults run 6 PM Mon/Tue/Wed/Fri and morning blocks on select days.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ss-home-section ss-home-section--flow ss-reveal" aria-labelledby="ss-home-flow-title">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="ss-home-story-grid">
          <article class="ss-home-flow-card ss-reveal delay-1">
            <span class="ss-home-kicker">Your First Visit</span>
            <h2 id="ss-home-flow-title">Your First Visit</h2>
            
            <p class="lead mb-3" style="font-family: var(--sans-font); font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--ss-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
              Meet Sandy, tour the training room, experience a guided introduction, and discover the class path that fits your goals. Every beginner receives a clear starting path.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4" style="font-family: var(--sans-font); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--ss-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
              Your first visit features guided, controlled partner work. Your first session features controlled partner activities, personal coaching, and an easy introduction to the movements and skills used in class. Progress at a pace that feels comfortable and sustainable.
            </p>
            
            <div class="mb-5">
              <a class="ss-btn ss-btn-primary ss-btn-island group" href="/book-free-intro" data-cta-target="intro"
                data-cta-label="Reserve a Free Intro" data-cta-src="home-first-visit"
                data-cta-placement="funnel_book" data-cta-tier="primary" data-cta-lane="mixed">
                <span class="ss-btn-text">Reserve a Free Intro</span>
                <span class="ss-btn-icon-wrapper">
                  <i class="bi bi-calendar2-event" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </span>
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="ss-home-steps" aria-label="First visit steps">
              <article class="ss-home-step">
